                    <span>To put it bluntly...Percey Boomer is God. Percey Boomer knows... but better yet Percy Boomer explains - perfectly...eloquently...amusingly...concisely.

The first lesson I had before I ever started playing was to read this book. In three months I broke 80. I still read this book.

If you understand what you're trying to do and you understand how to do it and you understand what it feels like when you're doing it right... Then you've read Percy Boomers - On Learning Golf</span>
                  
              
